      "created": "2019-10-15T12:13:31.317+0000",
      "description": "It would be nice if everywhere where a capacity can be defined could be defined the same way:\r\n * With fixed amounts (eg 1GB memory, 8 vcores, 3 GPU)\r\n * With percentages\r\n ** Percentage of all resources (eg 10% of all memory, vcore, GPU)\r\n ** Percentage per resource type (eg 10% memory, 25% vcore, 50% GPU)\r\n\r\nWe need to determine all configuration options where capacities can be defined, and see if it is possible to extend the configuration, or if it makes sense in that case.\r\n\r\nThe outcome is a proposal for all the configurations which could/should be changed.",
